<h4>{{ _('Powerinfo settings for Raspberry Pi') }}</h4>
{{ _('The plugin monitors the state of a 2 channel Raspberry Pi relay card (e.g. SainSmart).') }}<br />
<br />
<h5>{{ _('Input configuration') }}</h5>
{{ _('Specifiy the relay input pin on the pi (not the GPIO number).') }}<br />
<br />
<form class="form-horizontal">
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('relay 1') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <div class="input-append">
                <input type="number" step="1" min="1" max="40" class="input-mini text-right" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.powerinfo.inOnePin">
                <span class="add-on">Pin</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('relay 2') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <div class="input-append">
                <input type="number" step="1" min="1" max="40" class="input-mini text-right" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.powerinfo.inTwoPin">
                <span class="add-on">Pin</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>
<h5>{{ _('Web-Interface configuration') }}</h5>
{{ _('Specify the refresh rate of the plugin as well as the labels for the relays and states.') }}<br />
{{ _('Refresh rates lower than 5 seconds might impact overall performance!') }}<br />
<br />
<form class="form-horizontal">
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('refresh rate') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <div class="input-append">
                <input type="number" step="1" min="1" max="30" class="input-mini text-right" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.powerinfo.rRate">
                <span class="add-on">{{ _('seconds') }}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Label for power on') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.powerinfo.pwrOnName">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Label for power off') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.powerinfo.pwrOffName">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Label for relay 1') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.powerinfo.relayOneName">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <div class="controls">
            <label class="checkbox">
                <input type="checkbox" data-bind="checked: settings.plugins.powerinfo.showPwrOneStatus">{{ _('Show the relay state') }}
            </label>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Label for relay 2') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.powerinfo.relayTwoName">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <div class="controls">
            <label class="checkbox">
                <input type="checkbox" data-bind="checked: settings.plugins.powerinfo.showPwrTwoStatus">{{ _('Show the relay state') }}
            </label>
         </div>
    </div>
</form>
